'''2016年葛摩總統選舉'''在2016年4月10日舉行，初選則在2月21日進行<ref>[http://africanarguments.org/2016/02/18/presidential-elections-in-the-comoros-whose-turn-is-it-anyway/ Presidential Elections in the Comoros: Whose turn is it anyway?] {{Wayback|url=http://africanarguments.org/2016/02/18/presidential-elections-in-the-comoros-whose-turn-is-it-anyway/ |date=20160224011606 }} African Arguments, 18 February 2016</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.africanews.com/2016/04/04/comoros-key-presidential-poll-runoff-set-for-sunday-april-10/|title=Comoros: Key presidential poll runoff set for Sunday, April 10|website=africanews.channel|access-date=2016-04-05|archive-date=2018-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005003548/http://www.africanews.com/2016/04/04/comoros-key-presidential-poll-runoff-set-for-sunday-april-10/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==選舉制度==
選舉採用[[兩輪選舉制|兩輪選舉制]]投票，若是有候選人在首輪投票取得過半票數即確定當選<ref name=":0" />。

